---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="2026 Florida COA Board Member Survival Guide"
  description="Free guide covering the eight essentials every Florida condominium association board member must understand in 2026. Stay compliant with HB 1021, HB 913, and more."
>
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 via-primary-50/30 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 reveal">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-green-100 text-green-700 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-6">
          Free Resource
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
          2026 Florida COA Board Member <span class="gradient-text">Survival Guide</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          A step-by-step roadmap to staying compliant, organized, and effective—without the headaches.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Download Section -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-lg mb-12 reveal">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
          <div>
            <div class="text-6xl mb-4">&#128218;</div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Download Your Free Guide</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
              Eight essentials every Florida board member must understand in 2026. This practical guide addresses Florida's updated condominium laws with actionable solutions.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/The 2026 Florida COA Board Member Survival Guide.pdf"
              download
              class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-primary-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-all btn-shine"
            >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
              </svg>
              Download PDF Guide
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What's Inside:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Understanding HB 1021 & HB 913 requirements</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Reserve study and structural inspection deadlines</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Document retention requirements</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Board member certification timeline</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Meeting notice and voting procedures</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Financial reporting best practices</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Insurance requirements and liability</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Technology tools for modern boards</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Key Topics Section -->
      <div class="mb-12 reveal">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">Key Topics Covered</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm card-hover">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Florida Compliance</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Navigate HB 1021, HB 913, and other recent legislative changes affecting Florida COAs.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm card-hover">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Reserve Funding</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Understand new reserve requirements and how to prepare your association financially.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm card-hover">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-purple-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Structural Inspections</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Learn about milestone inspections and structural integrity reserve studies required for aging buildings.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm card-hover">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Document Management</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Best practices for organizing, storing, and accessing critical association documents.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <div class="text-center reveal">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-700 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Need help implementing these practices?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-primary-100 mb-6 max-w-xl mx-auto">
            CenturySync automates compliance tracking, document management, and board communication—so you can focus on your community.
          </p>
          <a href="/#demo" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-primary-700 font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all btn-shine">
            Schedule Your Demo
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
